column1: #Text=# Shape-Modeling-with-Spline-Partitions   The file contains code implements the shape modeling with spline partitions described in \*\*Ge, Shufei, Shijia Wang, and Lloyd Elliott.

#Text=The code files are released under the open source BSD 2-clause license.    ## Citation  If you use the code (partial or all) in your research, please cite the following manuscript: ```diff Ge, Shufei, Shijia Wang, and Lloyd Elliott.
